  "text": "The non-uniform triangulation of a three-dimensional domain represents a formidable numerical task. The concepts surveyed in this section are not new but combine various wellknown methods, and below, we will concentrate on the definitions necessary for the rest of this paper. For a more formal and complete introduction to tetrahedral triangulation see for example Ref. [CITATION_1] .",
